They may be much smaller than available elsewhere.
However the PPR does not have unlimited bandwidth.
Please selected when to download from the PPR 
based upon your Internet connection"

 A_HELP=$"Select this for slow, flaky and dial up connections"
 B_HELP=$"Select this for ISDN ADSL and download speeds less than 128K/sec"
